{\color{mediumblue}{\zitiAa\heiti 发展简史~}}
%
按照CTFS-ForestGEO样地建设技术规范，中国科学院生物多样性委员会于2004年正式启动“中国森林生物多样性监测网络（CForBio）”。2004$-$2007年，先后在长白山、古田山、鼎湖山、西双版纳建立4个大型样地；2009$-$2012年，在八大公山、弄岗、东灵山、宝天曼建立4个大型样地，与院外单位合作在丰林、凉水（红松林和云冷杉林）、天童、大兴安岭建立5个大型样地；到2016年底，在秦岭、穆棱、丽江、哀牢山和木论建立5个大型样地。另外还建立超过60个面积在1$-$5公顷的辅助样地。在2015年中国生物多样性监测与研究网络（Sino BON）成立后，CForBio成为Sino BON的子网络（Sino BON-CForBio）。
\\[0.9cm]
{\color{mediumblue}{\zitiAa\phv  Development History~}}
Organized by Biodiversity Committee, Chinese Academy of Sciences, the Chinese Forest Biodiversity Monitoring Network (CForBio) was established in 2004. From 2004 to 2007, 4 large plots in Changbaishan, Gutianshan, Dinghushan, and Xishuangbanna have been set up; form 2009 to 2012, 4 large plots in Badagongshan, Nonggang, Donglingshan, and Baotianman have been set up, and 5 large plots in Fenglin, Liangshui,Tiantong, and Daxinganling have been set up by cooperative institutes and universities. At the end of 2016, 4 large plots in Qinlin, Mulin, Lijiang, Ailaoshan, and Mulun have been set up. In addition it includes over 60 associated plots with the size 1--5 hm$\sffamily^\num{2}$. CForBio became Sino BON-CForBio as a sub network of Sino BON that was founded in 2015. 
%
\\[0.9cm]
%
{\color{mediumblue}{\zitiAa\heiti 科学计划~}}
\zitiB
\circled{1} 建成国家水平的森林生物多样性监测网络，对全国典型森林区域进行预警型监测；\circled{2} 探讨不同进化背景下地带性森林生物多样性的维持机制及变化效应；\circled{3} 为国家重大生态工程中生态恢复效果和生物多样性变化机理提供有效性监测和验证性监测。
\\[0.9cm]
{\color{mediumblue}{\zitiAa\phv  Science Initiative~}}
\zitiB
\circled{1} to establish forest biodiversity monitoring networks at the national scale for early warning monitoring the main forest areas; \circled{2} to explore mechanisms of biodiversity maintenance and effects of biodiversity change in different zonal forest regions and evolutionary backgrounds; \circled{3} to monitor the effectiveness of biodiversity conservation and validate the mechanisms of biodiversity change for key ecological conservation projects.\\[0.9cm]
